          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "USP_InvoiceHeaderRetrieve",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to retrieve invoice header information from a database. It accepts various parameters to filter the invoices and logs the operation details. The procedure uses a "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "TRY...CATCH",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " block to handle exceptions and logs both successful and failed attempts to retrieve invoice data."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
